.TH CLIPBOARD-MANAGER 1 "2025" "clipboard-manager" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
clipboard-manager \- clipboard history manager for Ubuntu
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B clipboard-manager
.SH DESCRIPTION
Clipboard Manager runs in the background and captures clipboard history.
Press Super+V at any time to see your recent clipboard items and paste
any of them into the currently focused window.
.SH FILES
.TP
~/.config/clipboard-manager/config.toml
User configuration file.
.SH AUTHOR
Clipboard Manager contributors.
